        "created_at": "2021-07-13T01:55:14.341Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi all,</p>\n<p>As Foundation DB is transactional, has any one implemented payment/banking system on top of it?<br>\nAnd how is the result ? or if not , as Foundation DB is ACID, is it really for this kind of jobs ?</p>\n<p>Have any one implemented Like/Dislike system (increment/decrement values) on top of it and how is the result for the same ?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
        "updated_at": "2021-07-13T02:15:09.379Z",
